{"story":{"group_1":[{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":1,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/general/3502_rec.ExportJson","zOrder":"messageBack"}],"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_21141.jpg","bgm":"bgm05_event07","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":101701,"motion":1,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305201,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":101701}],"nameRight":"Mitama","textRight":"This is... a very old story.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":101701}],"nameRight":"Mitama","textRight":"It all started back in the Kamakura period."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":305201,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Ashley","textLeft":"Kamakura...[chara:305201:lipSynch_0][wait:0.8][chara:305201:cheek_0][chara:305201:face_mtn_ex_010.exp.json][chara:305201:lipSynch_1]oh, the age of samurai!"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101701,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Mitama","textRight":"That's right..."},{"nameNarration":"Mitama","narration":"\"In a time of endless war,@there was a defeated soldier who fled the capital.\"","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101701}],"narration":"\"He dreamed of one day retaking the capital@and restoring it to its former glory, but...regrettably...@he met his end in the land of Kamihama...\""},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101701,"motion":300}],"narration":"\"However...@That fallen warrior never realized that he was dead...\""},{"narration":"\"He still wanders Kamihama to this day,@longing to return to his homeland...\""},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305201,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Ashley","narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"That's a sad story..."},{"nameCenter":"Riko's voice","textCenter":"It's sad...but I'm glad it wasn't that scary."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101701,"lipSynch":0}],"nameRight":"Mitama","textRight":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":101701,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Mitama","textRight":"Excuse me... If you don't mind me asking..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"black","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"Mitama","narration":"\"Which way is the capital...?\"","narrationBg":"black","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_21141.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":305201,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101701,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":101701,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Mitama","textRight":"What if the person who hears that...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":101701}],"nameRight":"Mitama","textRight":"...is taken directly to the other side?"},{"chara":[{"id":305201,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Ashley","textLeft":"[chara:305201:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]...?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305201,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"Ashley","textLeft":"T-to the other side...?"},{"nameCenter":"Riko's voice","textCenter":"Eek...! Th-that means..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101701}],"nameRight":"Mitama","textRight":"...Yes, that means they'll be cursed to death."},{"nameCenter":"Riko's voice","textBg":"shout","textCenter":"Eeeeek...!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":305201,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Ashley","textBg":"shout","textLeft":"I'm shook!!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305201}],"nameLeft":"Ashley","textLeft":"A Japanese vengeful spirit! There's a curse?! "},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":101701,"motion":1},{"id":305201,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Mitama","textRight":"...Yes."},{"nameNarration":"Mitama","narration":"\"In the olden days...@Many people were disappearing, and those remaining@feared they'd been cursed by the fallen warrior.@So, they built and tended to a memorial tomb@with great care.\"","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"\"Thus... Nothing happened for a while, but...\""},{"narration":"\"Not long ago,@a big company tried to tear down the tomb@and build an apartment building.\""},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101701,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"Mitama","narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"Since then, the fallen warrior has@begun appearing once more..."},{"chara":[{"id":101701}],"nameRight":"Mitama","textRight":"There are people being taken by the@fallen warrior...[chara:101701:lipSynch_0][wait:0.8][chara:101701:eyeClose_1][chara:101701:lipSynch_1]you know?"},{"nameCenter":"Riko's voice","textCenter":"Eek...!"},{"chara":[{"id":305201,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Ashley","textBg":"shout","textLeft":"They can't tear it down!@They're gonna get cursed!!"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101701,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"Mitama","textRight":"The apartments were never completed..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101701}],"nameRight":"Mitama","textRight":"Some say that the fallen warrior still@lingers there..."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bg":"bg_adv_11091.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305201,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51126_tower_Ashley/51126_kumanosuke.png","posX":300,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"Ashley","narration":"\"In Japanese horror stories,@there are often fallen warriors.\"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305201}],"narration":"\"And that's because...\""},{"chara":[{"id":305201,"motion":300}],"narration":"\"Even if soldiers flee after losing a battle,@their pursuers may find and kill them...\""},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":305201}],"narration":"\"Many of them meet their end while full of regrets...\""},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":3052